flowchart TD
    A[User Request] --> B{Authentication}
    B -->|Valid| C[Load Balancer]
    B -->|Invalid| D[Error Page]
    C --> E[API Gateway]
    E --> F{Route Parser}
    F -->|/users| G[User Service]
    F -->|/orders| H[Order Service]
    F -->|/payments| I[Payment Service]
    F -->|/notifications| J[Notification Service]
    G --> K[(User DB)]
    G --> L[(Redis Cache)]
    H --> M[(Order DB)]
    H --> N[Inventory Check]
    N --> O{In Stock?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Process Order]
    O -->|No| Q[Backorder]
    P --> I
    I --> R[Payment Gateway]
    R --> S{Payment OK?}
    S -->|Yes| T[Confirm Order]
    S -->|No| U[Retry Payment]
    U --> R
    T --> J
    J --> V[Email Service]
    J --> W[SMS Service]
    J --> X[Push Notification]
    V --> Y[Success Response]
    W --> Y
    X --> Y
    Q --> J
